Package m2mimud.command

Interface Summary
CommandExec The CommandExec interface is used to designate a class which can accept command for processing.
 

Class Summary
Command The command class is an object representation the command which the user entered.
IntCommand The IntCommand class is for commands which have an associated string value.
Parser The Parser is the object that takes in the string value typed in by the user and creates a Command object that can be given to the GameSystem to tell it what to do to perform the user's action
StringCommand The StringCommand class is for commands which have an associated string value.
StringIntCommand The StringIntCommand is for commands which carry both a string and it value.
